        {
            "id": 6318367,
            "title": "投信近3日買超個股",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>1. 投信累計買超 3 日的股票<br/>元大高股息 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:0056:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/0056\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">0056-TW</a>)、群創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3481:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3481\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3481-TW</a>)、南電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8046:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8046\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8046-TW</a>)、台新新光金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2887:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2887\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2887-TW</a>)、國巨 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2327:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2327\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2327-TW</a>)</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>2. 投信累計買超 2 日的股票<br/>元大高股息 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:0056:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/0056\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">0056-TW</a>)、群創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3481:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3481\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3481-TW</a>)、南電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8046:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8046\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8046-TW</a>)、矽力-KY (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6415:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6415\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6415-TW</a>)、欣興 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3037:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3037\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3037-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>3. 投信當日 (21) 買超的股票<br/>群創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3481:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3481\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3481-TW</a>)、元大高股息 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:0056:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/0056\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">0056-TW</a>)、元大台灣50 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:0050:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/0050\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">0050-TW</a>)、南電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8046:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8046\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8046-TW</a>)、景碩 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3189:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3189\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3189-TW</a>)<br/> </p></section></main>",
